{"tid":2514174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門獨立屋遭爆竊　警拔槍拘三賊","createTime":"2021-05-03T05:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T10:09:28.000Z","uid":63909,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0efabad8a8d50ccfbe1958bf28ea086b71dfd691","tid":2514174,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"屯門發生爆竊案，警員到場拔槍拘捕三人，兩名警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n大批機動部隊警員在現場一帶蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚九時許，屯門新慶村一間獨立屋被賊人入屋爆竊，警員接報到場，有人用伸縮警棍企圖襲警，警員拔槍戒備，<strong>當場拘捕三名疑犯，其中兩人是內地人，另一人趁機逃去</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n兩名警員制服疑犯時，手腳擦傷拒絕送院。警方在附近發現一輛私家車，懷疑與案件有關。單位經點算後，損失一批金器、首飾及珠寶，總值約二十二萬元及一萬三千元現金。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433310&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=c9c65b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433310&h=9b737de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433310</a><br />\n專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e241571e0a8fea158373571aae667410f0cd2c90","tid":2514174,"uid":392446,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"又自編自導自演"},{"pid":"05937b540eced3da4ec2b60786af04137bd31120","tid":2514174,"uid":78039,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"點解d賊手腳咁慢"},{"pid":"39105e0f8375bf84bb6f54b0da2cfe22a5e367cb","tid":2514174,"uid":143241,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"又話黨安法繁榮安定嘅？安定去咗邊？"},{"pid":"36b24810994f38ae99be795e5034f29f40ca4c73","tid":2514174,"uid":85396,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"又話有國安法好安全既<br />\n點解仲多左嫁<br />\n禾地藍絲又書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal